{
  "stem": "26111.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was, I think, the parents because I talked with the parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, understanding that I was a somewhat more grown-up child, spoke to me accordingly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I asked questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the one-- the one saving grace in this whole situation, that I had somebody I can ask questions of besides my parents, who, in that sense, were not too, too helpful, not, not-- through none of their fault.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we had-- for example, for Seder, this was a-- at Passover, we-- it was a tradition.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have Passover at our house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we went to the house of very close friends, very close family of friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that is where I learned the-- that particular tradition, and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "With, with-- by being in a context, in a social context, that was not-- certainly not entirely, but to a large extent-- to a sufficiently large extent-- Jewish, it helped me to get answers to the questions, find out where the Habonim is, find out what a Zionist was, find out what my parents were, politically speaking.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was-- they were referred to by one friend as a-- my father was referred to as a CV, which is not 'curriculum vitae.' What it stood for was Centralverein, which is Central Association of Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was the conservative branch, the non-Zionist branch, the assimilationist branch, which was very powerful politically.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, and then there were the Zionist-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Zionist wing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know what the adult organizations were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I knew about the youth organizations, Maccabi and the Habonim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It had not anything to do with that, I'm afraid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It, it, it had a-- [SIGHS] I, I was a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
